t, maybe using catch could work due to dynamic class loading? I need to focus on that target call, which is all about dynamic class loading. Hmm, it might be helpful to check the test-results-native to see if they currently all pass. This could guide my next steps in figuring out what to do.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0e284eda8ac4086b0169fb757edc3881a3be477f353987310a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-3WOYCD1Iyc2Qe0mTlDjjbrbadz0Ej8WLmV05Mjb7a9dOU6VX4tZemiUn3YpmTB8b3Fy69IUxsoMnDF2Pq5Vvl-pJ0spJgA6VYv-7CXaxXZBDvHuazdIQq7S8doDkMw-NqbcrKfc5DLtzg1ZbYnRYITjtsltjDs791Y6h3liQVWnDfQJhrjm1bt10ZCNNEH2nSjEGBnIWtP00u4MOHxspVlpg3ihVMvmQwtAzFYf9vRQxqXC8_SJTCEwo8C8w7u22M3VSCl4sCEJBA1QUHnIIQv9A0HVd90CVsJstyuKsRzNz2m98wT9J5LKP4Gf1lDkuwAfpEpr3pNRns_s71-NyPrnU3fbxEB4oKLDNUwcdVTu4_X49E6LpIfcFsIIQDJ7vpvypkq4yzBCxJHxG4DC8aNRvMTj8ZRdxp1Oo1kHgoQoLPJ3j7mkwy6YpwOhdY7yToJf1bmlntKW0T-WffPbs0PhC68UZ4lpoQtxMfNOZGTPMYb2pVY4RtcwHievJeXD6ZC9Cup6s89MJsrtIRDGnvJpIFSF750-5SduyJXZ1Swytb_t4ItmMsyVpeocQnEejtTeSMpe5uU1AXg68uOwFDu0pZD4QkIGRetTxzFyP-WLa6KKFezAImydfQUVeTeIL_8TdsoKDwEGlCIV9-SHSL4il3lBUZAWXAeZe0yExkhbSB_ZMG6B_FXjHSa1aNUs7mQX9pd9aLocGCJPk8N9ro9t8pH3emr_-YLZRBa7qhSlbn3OIHkS7dn-wjYGnrKFgux6OnYiBGa0ToZLAFjhHBsyV1DaztknW1vW7rVzOo9LfTPOf7cVEA4rw4t04u74YpTAhdrAqE2XlbHiyyamMgL2613edQGHal9o3itSF9KKI-4_Vd752Yz0BRnNTahF-wdklUNpxfdqmdm7gNA_8EKkY7JLThngxB5fkqBuIL8idwog50ZoMmhGeZPWi5UXnjeP0wCzpqnq5EIQinqh5fqkNwLjaustbOcKHt8lxGR17uRMTR-sk3xFfmN8gIHeVjDybJgJkICT3ZgzWjCebaVc7EhebP7Wbj9DS7DqRUJZNm1l4N2ZfKkV1cfJCpt5vQ6r0TF7mWRDH32gYDGuOoJYZeI3_NWdrrwdSN7Om1EJY6GTgGs2uSKCtjqNQRPD0UUo8_6qCT3Hwu9vHBkOAjpjRHrgI9BCnmCwbSki12i8ZZqbnM-pYAfumGIlysnAdNAR2gbUz17fQAjYUAPgb7CFLRUUENCGuYtOPSuIuCuYqIPWKC_to4cWNK-WloJE9StLud4-MpoHchOk0bxbwqoATsfefL2T9koZer9QgamYK0H2eQATdojlVsipt3Xk7PaGzd1eY2HQ5i3f6dQ29Bvy6grJdLGxk_qzx9ser8hWcyM_3Q2sUJhanSMtrL5Qqi2Zr8qARz_r0QGHgW9i8UT5fJhrruyBlLiPy-YbwpyGwRa8m_DIFRCaDCfYrXpsPFhSyvyxgelnv_Qbw4avCkm5n4xvlagRkGsP939fjjPG07Cgh7u7_9cNGjcN88anBRevHd0uSer4xsMySA6_i99W7X